Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] The ANC's [African National Congress] draft plan 
to revamp the mining industry has not only caused ripples 
locally. Internationally it has also being labeled as 
nationalization. Share prices on the Johannesburg Stock 
Exchange plunged sharply right after the announcement with the 
