<H3> <TI>   UN Notes Confinement of 599 Government, 58 Renamo Soldiers </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB2001165194 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 
1400 GMT 20 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB2001165194 </F>
<F P=104>  Maputo Radio Mozambique Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The UN Operations in Mozambique's daily report says 
599 government soldiers and 58 Mozambique National Resistance 
