<H3> <TI>   Radio Reports Bongo `Finally' Sworn-In 22 Jan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AB2201140594 Libreville RTG Chaine Nationale Radio Network 
in French 1200 GMT 22 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> AB2201140594 </F>
<F P=104>  Libreville RTG Chaine Nationale Radio Network 
